.SH ERRORS
All errors raise exceptions that inherit from
.B pyax25_22.core.exceptions.AX25Error.
.PP
Frame parsing errors raise
.B FrameError
or a subclass (InvalidAddressError, FCSError, BitStuffingError).
.PP
State machine violations raise
.B ConnectionStateError.
.PP
Transport failures raise
.B KISSError
or
.B AGWPEError.
.PP
Configuration errors raise
.B ConfigurationError.
